PROCESS IS ONE YOU CAN TRUST
WHEN YOU CAN'T TRUST EACH OTHER.

03:11.824 --> 03:18.298
>> Pelley: PHILLIP GOFF IS A
PROFESSOR OF AFRICAN AMERICAN
STUDIES, WITH A Ph.D. IN
PSYCHOLOGY.

03:18.364 --> 03:26.673
