05:13.880 --> 05:19.952
MURDERED IN MINNEAPOLIS IN 2020,
AUSTIN WAS ALREADY SMOLDERING
OVER TWO POLICE KILLINGS OF ITS
OWN.

05:20.019 --> 05:29.295
TWO COPS ARE CHARGED WITH MURDER
IN SHOOTINGS, NINE MONTHS APART,
OF A MENTAL PATIENT, AND AN
UNARMED MAN WHO WAS BLACK AND

05:29.362 --> 05:37.937
LATINO.
