GIVE POLICE LESS TO DO-- BY
SPENDING THE MONEY ON ADDICTION,

06:02.628 --> 06:10.670
MENTAL ILLNESS AND HOMELESSNESS.
AUSTIN CALLED IT "REIMAGINING
PUBLIC SAFETY."
>> Goff: LAW ENFORCEMENT IS NOT

06:10.737 --> 06:16.943
GOING TO PREVENT THE VIOLENCE.
THEY'RE GOING TO RESPOND TO IT.
AND IF WHAT YOU WANT IS LESS
VIOLENCE, YOU WANT PREVENTION.

06:17.009 --> 06:25.418
>> Pelley: WHEN PEOPLE HEAR
ABOUT REIMAGINING THE POLICE,
THAT SEEMS TO COME UNDER THE
SLOGAN OF DEFUNDING THE POLICE.

06:25.485 --> 06:30.790
AND I THINK MANY PEOPLE LOOK AT
THAT AND THINK, "MY COMMUNITY'S
GOING TO BE LESS SAFE."
>> Goff: I THINK THERE ARE

06:30.857 --> 06:37.130
COMMUNITIES WHERE THAT'S
ABSOLUTELY TRUE.
<i>OF COURSE,</i> YOU WOULD BE.
BUT, WE'VE DEFUNDED THE SCHOOLS

06:37.196 --> 06:40.867
IN THOSE COMMUNITIES.
WE'VE DEFUNDED MENTAL HEALTH.
WE'VE DEFUNDED THE ACTUAL
HOSPITALS.

06:40.933 --> 06:44.070
WE'VE DEFUNDED THE JOBS.
WE'VE DEFUNDED THE HOUSING
SYSTEM.
WE'VE DEFUNDED THE GROCERY

06:44.137 --> 06:49.976
STORES.
WHAT IF, INSTEAD OF TALKING
ABOUT<i> JUST</i> DEFUNDING POLICE,
WE TALKED ABOUT<i> RE-FUNDING</i> TO

06:50.042 --> 06:54.781
THE COMMUNITIES, THOSE<i> AREAS</i>
WHERE WE'VE TAKEN ALL THE
RESOURCES AND THE PUBLIC GOODS
AWAY?

06:54.847 --> 07:01.954
IF WE DID THAT, HOW MUCH SAFER
DO YOU THINK WE WOULD BE?
THE REASON WHY PEOPLE ARE SO
ALLERGIC TO THE IDEA OF LESS

07:02.021 --> 07:07.960
POLICE IS, THEY CAN'T IMAGINE A
WORLD WHERE WE TAKE<i> BETTER</i> CARE
OF THE PEOPLE WHO ARE
VULNERABLE.

07:08.027 --> 07:13.966
