BECAUSE, BEFORE AUSTIN, HE RAN

07:54.907 --> 08:02.682
THE CITY OF MINNEAPOLIS.
HE LEFT TWO YEARS BEFORE GEORGE
FLOYD WAS MURDERED.
>> Cronk: IT IS ONE OF THOSE

08:02.748 --> 08:11.190
TIMES IN WHICH YOU KNOW THAT
THINGS HAVE TO CHANGE.
>> Pelley: CRONK STARTED THAT
CHANGE BY SHUTTING DOWN THE

08:11.257 --> 08:18.798
AUSTIN POLICE ACADEMY FOR A
