THERE, SOMEONE WHO'S ACTUALLY

12:04.256 --> 12:09.195
TRAINED IN SUBSTANCE ABUSE?
MENTAL HEALTH STUFF.
HOW ABOUT WE SEND SOMEONE WHO'S
TRAINED IN THAT, TO GO DO THAT?"

12:09.261 --> 12:13.566
AND WE'RE STARTING TO CUT AWAY
AT THE THINGS WE'VE ASKED LAW
ENFORCEMENT TO DO, THAT THEY
DON'T WANT TO DO.

12:13.632 --> 12:21.273
>> AUSTIN 911, WHAT'S YOUR
EMERGENCY?
