NEED TO CONCENTRATE ON THAT, AND
NOT ON ANY FALSE NARRATIVE THERE
MIGHT BE ABOUT HOW POLICING IS

14:05.911 --> 14:10.683
JUST ABSOLUTELY BROKEN.
CAN WE DO THINGS BETTER?
CERTAINLY.
BUT THERE'S MANY THINGS THAT I

14:10.749 --> 14:18.691
THINK THAT WE DO VERY WELL.
>> Pelley: THE PERIOD AFTER
